works.description: Old school gamers are going to love this thing for sure. If you are retro gaming fan and love to play Neo Geo or have always wanted to, a company called Analogue Interactive has a treat for you. The firm has given the SNK’s classic home console a custom, wooden makeover, and has christened it the Neo Geo Consolized MVS. The Consolized MVS (CMVS), made with 100 percent real walnut wood, shares the same form and functionality as of the SNK’s original NeoGeo home console. The Consolized MVS has been sealed internally and externally with six layers of high quality lacquer.
